data.description: This 3-bed, 3.5-bath, 1.5-story home in Milan is a nature lover's dream! Nestled on nearly an acre of wooded land, this home is sure to grab your attention. From the front porch you enter the living room with it's vaulted ceilings & floor-to-ceiling stacked stone accent wall. The open floor plan connecting the living room, dining room, & lofted family room make the space bright & airy. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances & a reverse osmosis system. Nice hardwood floors lead you into the formal dining room, complete with a fireplace. Upstairs you'll discover a large lofted family room, the primary bedroom with direct access to the guest bathroom, & the 2nd bedroom with its own private bath. The 3rd bedroom is located in the walk-out basement, along with a rec room & 3rd full bath. The true highlight of the home is the backyard! With 3 levels of decks & 5 way to access them from the inside, you are sure to find the perfect spot to see wildlife pass through your wooded lot. Don't let this home slip through your fingers!
